43695.name: Time spent in domestic work, female (hours)
43695.description: Time spent in domestic work, female refers to average hours per day that women ages 20-74 spent on housework, child and adult care, gardening and pet care, construction and repairs, shopping and services, and household management. Data are reported in number of hours, where decimals represent hundredths of an hour (e.g, 1.75 should be read 1 hour and 45 minutes; 0.20 should be read 12 minutes).
